# Backup in Znuny

Daliy backups of the entire server
## Software

Veeam Agent for Linux (free Edition)

Job name: FullServer
                       Destination │
                       Network     │ Destination: //192.168.147.105/Veeambackups
                       Schedule    │ Backup: Entire computer
                     > Summary     │ Schedule: Daily at 00:30
                                   │
                                   │ To start the job out of schedule execute:
                                   │ veeamconfig job start --name "FullServer"
